Highways
The four expressways in the prefecture connect major cities with other prefectures .
The Matsue expressway connects Matsue with Unnan and Yonago in Tottori prefecture .
Hamada Expressway forks from the Chugoku Expressway at Kita-Hiroshima and stretches to Hamada .
